name: SpaceX Launch Facility - Boca Chica, Texas September 2019 - Infrared
description: An original infrared photograph of the SpaceX launch facility at Boca Chica, Texas  on September 12, 2019. As can be seen, the Starhopper sits on its pad after a successful launch one month earlier as well as construction of the fueling farm being carried on nearby. At the far left can be seen the actual SpaceX rocket construction and assembly facility, about a mile away. Photograph taken with a Canon T1i modified for infrared photography, and an 850nm infrared filter.
